nodes.text: Treasure Ship Row, or simply the Row, was a large, open-air shopping mall located in Coronet City's Blue Sector on Corellia. The shop was always filled with crowds of people, as Treasure Ship Row offered everything for consumers. From food shops to clothing stores to cantinas (such as the Fel Swoop) to antique stores, Treasure Ship Row was one of Coronet's finer locations, despite its location in Coronet's notoriously dangerous Blue Sector. It was located near an apartment complex.
The Corellian Security Force used the nickname "Dirtdock" for Treasure Ship Row.
